102
00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:36.364
<i>sampai matahari terbit</i>

103
00:09:36.364 --> 00:09:38.735
<i>dan tanah akan mengering.</i>

104
00:09:40.044 --> 00:09:42.048
<i>Di Seoul sekarang,</i>

105
00:09:42.048 --> 00:09:44.708
<i>hujan turun tanpa peringatan.</i>

106
00:09:46.614 --> 00:09:48.871
<i>Apakah itu tanda kesedihan</i>

107
00:09:48.871 --> 00:09:51.117
<i>apa yang Tuhan kirimkan kepada kita?</i>

108
00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.204
<i>Kamu,</i>

109
00:09:54.204 --> 00:09:56.710
<i>apakah mereka membawa payung?</i>

110
00:10:01.786 --> 00:10:04.247
Dia juga memainkan Bom seperti ini,

111
00:10:04.247 --> 00:10:06.860
